SUMMARY:Red Dead Redemption II | Ep. 10 - Outlaws, Dust, and a Debt to
 Settle
DESCRIPTION:Back into the Wild West, where unfinished business always
 comes back around. Expect tension, storytelling, and tough decisions.
 Arthur Morgan and the Van der Linde Gang are outlaws on the run. With
 federal agents and bounty hunters massing on their heels, the gang must
 rob, steal, and fight their way across the rugged heartland in order to
 survive.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cy-GgST5ZxU
CATEGORIES:Red Dead Redemption II
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
