LAST-MODIFIED:20260409T211300Z
DTSTART:20260404T203000Z
DTEND:20260404T223000Z
SUMMARY:Fallout 4 | Ep. 42 - The Only Theme Park With More Bullets Than
 Rides
DESCRIPTION:Nuka-World continues to be exactly as safe as you'd expect -
 which is to say, not safe at all. More chaos, more danger, more
 questionable choices. As the sole survivor of Vault 111, you enter a world
 destroyed by nuclear war. Every second is a fight for survival, and every
 choice is yours. Only you can rebuild and determine the fate of the
 Wasteland. Welcome home.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pU0UHbDmTrQ
CATEGORIES:Fallout 4
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
