SUMMARY:The Last Caretaker | Ep. 1 - Maintaining the End of the World, One
 Task at a Time
DESCRIPTION:A brand-new series begins! We step into a mysterious role at
 the end of the world - keeping things running... or at least trying to.
 Explore a drowned Earth, restore lost systems, and raise the last human
 seeds in this first-person survival-crafting adventure. Build, scavenge,
 defend, and launch humanity back to the stars.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pF_VNK9V5Hw
CATEGORIES:The Last Caretaker
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
