SUMMARY:Sniper Elite V2 Remastered | Ep. 8 - Kreuzberg Headquarters
DESCRIPTION:Precision continues. One careful shot can change everything...
 or alert absolutely everyone. In the dark days of the end of World War 2
 amidst the ruins of Berlin, one bullet can change history... Elite sniper
 Karl Fairburne returns to the front line in the remaster of this
 award-winning stealth-action experience. Packed with new features,
 contemporary visuals and definitive content.
