BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-23012211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260326T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260409T211300Z
DTSTART:20260416T203000Z
DTEND:20260416T223000Z
SUMMARY:Final Fantasy Mystic Quest | Ep. 1 - The \"Easy\" Final Fantasy...
 Is It Actually Good?
DESCRIPTION: Step into one of the most unique entries in the Final Fantasy
 series with Final Fantasy Mystic Quest, known in Europe as Mystic Quest
 Legend. Originally released on the SNES, this classic RPG was designed as
 an accessible introduction to the genre-making it perfect for both
 newcomers and retro fans.\n\nJoin me as I explore its colorful world,
 battle iconic monsters, and rediscover a game that often flies under the
 radar in the Final Fantasy lineup. With its simplified mechanics,
 memorable soundtrack, and nostalgic 16-bit charm, Mystic Quest offers a
 laid-back RPG experience that's all about fun and exploration.\n\nWhether
 you played this back in the day or you're seeing it for the first time,
 come hang out, relax, and enjoy some retro vibes as we journey through
 this hidden gem together.
URL:https://www.twitch.tv/dr_ravenholm
CATEGORIES:Final Fantasy Mystic Quest
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
